Subject: Secunia Research: Blazix Web Server JSP Source Code Disclosure
	Vulnerability


====================================================================== 

                    Secunia Research 28/03/2006

    - Blazix Web Server JSP Source Code Disclosure Vulnerability -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

